          "content": "I can help, but I donâ€™t have live news access in this chat.\n\nIf you want the latest news in Iran right now, the fastest reliable options are:\n\n- Reuters Iran coverage: https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/\n- AP News Middle East: https://apnews.com/hub/middle-east\n- BBC News Middle East: https://www.bbc.com/news/world/middle_east\n- Al Jazeera Iran tag: https://www.aljazeera.com/tag/iran/\n- Iran International: https://www.iranintl.com/en\n\nIf you want, I can still help in one of these ways:\n1. Summarize recent major Iran developments I'm aware of\n2. Help you verify whether a specific Iran headline is credible\n3. Give you a quick briefing format to track politics, economy, protests, regional tensions, and nuclear talks\n\nIf you want a quick briefing, I can format it like:\n- Politics\n- Economy/currency\n- Regional/security\n- Nuclear/diplomacy\n- Domestic unrest/social issues\n\nIf you paste a headline or article, Iâ€™ll summarize it and tell you what matters.",
